---

This project includes code adapted from OpenCode
(https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode)

Copyright (c) Anomaly Co.
Licensed under the MIT License

Components derived from OpenCode include:
- Theme system and theme files (src/context/theme/)
- Keybind handling (src/context/keybind.tsx)
- KV store pattern (src/context/kv.tsx, src/lib/kv.ts)
- Dialog system (src/components/dialog.tsx)
- Tool renderers (src/components/message/tool-renderers/)
- Clipboard utilities with OSC52 (src/util/clipboard.ts)
- ASCII logo with shadow rendering (src/components/logo.tsx)
- Tips component (src/components/tips.tsx)
- Toast notifications (src/components/toast.tsx)
- Route management (src/context/route.tsx)
- Exit handling (src/context/exit.tsx)
